{"tid":470314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男仔鐘意咩性格嘅女仔做女朋友/老婆呢？","createTime":"2017-11-16T07:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T13:34:57.000Z","uid":17633,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"455b911be7a718e22db8a3df119e2bec5d6d24c8","tid":470314,"uid":17633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:41:24.000Z","msg":"唔計外表<br />\n<br />\n第一種<br />\n獨立自主型，有咩問題都唔會煩到你，識自己解決，適當時候會溫柔體貼<br />\n<br />\n但呢類女性通常唔太識嗲人，係佢身上唔會有被需要嘅感覺，滿足唔到男性想保護柔弱嘅天性<br />\n<br />\n第二種<br />\n小鳥依人型，幾時都咁嬌嗲<br />\n<br />\n但份人會比較冇主見，會好依賴你，大小事都要你幫佢解決<br />\n<br />\n唔講得咁極端啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩種都會有時發吓脾氣attention seeking,但佢好愛你<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家cm討論<br />\n<br />\n因為以我所知有啲男仔都好唔鐘意自己女朋友成日問東問西，毫無主見，太依賴，但又驚佢太痴身會好煩"},{"pid":"bec1f7296a050eb7fbc5ba4af8b4ec296ef00b86","tid":470314,"uid":38668,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"女朋友都冇, 點答阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36da71bfe923543d87347ff4b9fbde2dd7de670","tid":470314,"uid":47584,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"兩種性格各一半就perfect<br />\n適當時候出聲 適當時候收聲<br />\n呢一樣係好多女人都要學既野<br />\n<br />\n對我嚟講<br />\n識得揀岩時間出聲好重要<br />\n唔鍾意女人太煩"},{"pid":"79e024c3496c05f96b2c49dcb4528f4f5ae1a1e4","tid":470314,"uid":17633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女朋友都冇, 點答阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你期望未來遇到嘅女朋友呢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cac4788574cad1eea357db8cc74d377e7be7e26","tid":470314,"uid":74262,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b72760ae9e7d137b51a4723f07455f69ccbc644","tid":470314,"uid":17633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>